HEADWORD: Demulce
<hw>De*mulce"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>demulcere</ets>; <ets>de-</ets> + <ets>mulcere</ets> to stroke,
soothe.]</ety> <def>To soothe; to mollify; to pacify; to soften.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Sir T. Elyot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
